translated: Dellborg, Johannes Georg, lawyer, Gothenburg, born on 27/6/97 in Gothenburg. Married in 1928 to Dagmar Hariette Kjällman. Children: Rolf born in 1929, Stig born in 1935. He graduated from Gothenburg Latin School in 1917 and from Uppsala University with a law degree in 1922. He worked as a court clerk in Flundre, Väne and Bjärke from 1922-1925, then started his own law firm in 1925. From 1925-1940, he worked as a deputy lawyer in the law firm Drakenberg & von Sneidern in Gothenburg and became a co-owner in 1940. He was chairman of the Gothenburg district sports association and a board member of the Swedish Ski Association from 1942. He was also chairman of the Ski Promotion Gothenburg division from 1943. He became a member of the Swedish Bar Association in 1929.
